    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 1731.2, y: -595.2}
    <Text>k__BackingField: When America was founded, physical strength was required
      to acquire more land. Hence, such traits are admired. This was further deepened
      as throughout American history, there were quite a few wars, such as the Civil
      War. Hence, such traits were held in high regard.
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
